::: {#cell-andon-lamp .cell execution_count=1}
``` {.python .cell-code}
from solid import *
from solid.utils import *
import viewscad

width = 210
height = 36
depth = 304
thickness = 15
button_radius = 15
stick_radius = 12
button_translations = [
    [44, 174, height + thickness],  # 1
    [82, 174, height + thickness],  # 3
    [214, 174, height + thickness],  # 0
    [252, 174, height + thickness],  # =
    [186, 156, height + thickness],  # i
    [280, 156, height + thickness],  # \
    [182, 100, height + thickness],  # spacebar
    [154, 82, height + thickness],  # extra
]
stick_translation = [62, 118, height + thickness]

top = up(height + thickness)(cube([depth, width, thickness]))
bottom = cube([depth, width, thickness])
side = rotate([90, 0, 0])((cube([depth, height, thickness])))
front = translate([0, thickness, thickness])(side)
back = translate([0, width - thickness, 0])(front)

side = cube([thickness, depth - 4 * thickness, height])
left = translate([0, thickness, thickness])(side)

button = cylinder(r=button_radius, h=thickness).set_hole(True)
stick = cylinder(r=stick_radius, h=thickness).set_hole(True)

for translation in button_translations:
    top += translate(translation)(button)
top += translate(stick_translation)(stick)

parts = [top, bottom, front, back, left]
piece = sum(parts)

viewscad.Renderer().render(piece)
```
